The paper discusses the security and performance of private blockchain systems, which are relevant to the categories of cryptography (cs.CR), distributed computing (cs.DC), databases (cs.DB), software engineering (cs.SE), and distributed systems (cs.Distributed Systems). However, since the focus is on evaluating and comparing different private blockchain platforms, the most likely categories are cs.CR and cs.DC, followed by cs.DB, cs.SE, and cs.Distributed Systems.
